Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The history of games can be traced back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the way to Ancient Egypt 5,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These ancient games decided the fate of the citizens and the kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They were called the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the time where a boy has solved the Millennium Puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and released the Dark Games has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A boy with both a heart of light and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People refer to him as Yuugiou: The Game King.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Pegasus... He intends to take over the Kaiba Corporation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear! The Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... that's really my brother's deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, Yugi Mutou's duel data is stored inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, there's a need of a password in order to enter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work! Get inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(307,143)}Blue-Eyes White Dragon Strikes Back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn. I play this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It didn't appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have three silk hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can defeat the Black Magician,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Life Points will decrease. However, under one of the silk hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've put a trap card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... what's he planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His chances are one in three!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! The middle one! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hexagram Curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes is really almost invincible... but there's a method to reduce his attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Go! Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon is defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician is defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In all my deck there're three Blue-Eyes White Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be that you've forgotten, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, is Kaiba really dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are afraid of me. Of my spirit that has revived from the dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason that you made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Yugi, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...that's not the reality! My brother is definitely alive! Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The security system was frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The central control room's alarm was set off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The virtual system was unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From now on, our access mode can be detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore it. Keep on going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Successfully entered booth 146!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi Mutou's duel data found!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Image!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's fighting Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The name displayed is "Seto Kaiba"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Identity unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're not only using my deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but my name as well for a duel like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the situation of the duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Presently in the field there's the second Blue-Eyes White Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first one was defeated by a combo attack from Black Magician and Magical Silk Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He defeated a Blue-Eyes without using Exodia... Yugi... as expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, now he has no way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes. He has no cards capable of defeating this second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means it's a desperate situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a way. Now we will decrease the second Blue-Eyes's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He already played it on the field, so we can't do anything to the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can infect the monster's apparition with a virus, his attack should decrease.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please set the virus level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maximum! Start attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood. Starting virus infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no card in my hand that can defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally realized?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and play a monster for the Blue-Eyes to destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as the Seal Defense card is in play,\N I can't put monsters in defense mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gremlin in attack mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gremlin has appeared in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Blue-Eyes starts the next attack, it will all be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Virus infection at 50%. It seems the Blue-Eyes still wasn't affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Infection in 70%
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blue-Eyes's attack didn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally it's time to end this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Isn't there something that we can do, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you want {\i1}me{\i0} to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon.... attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Infection has reached 95%
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blue-Eyes White Dragon's attack is decreasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It's started to work. Reduce it! Reduce more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Blue-Eyes...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact the central room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto Kaiba is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Virus infection reached 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:09:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blue-Eyes White Dragon's attack is currently 2300. Continuing to reduce.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Prepare to attack the third one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It froze. Attack's reduction stopped. Unknown reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello Kaiba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blue-Eyes's attack's reduction stopped at 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Burst Stream has been fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot it Blue Eyes! Burst Stream!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YUGI!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YUGI!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unfrozen. Blue-Eyes White Dragon's destruction confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be. Hey, can you say how this happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't. Unknown reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what the heart of the cards is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba... is alive... he is....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Seto Kaiba is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious, isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one other than my brother that could destroy the Blue-Eyes like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my brother's doing! I knew it! My brother is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's proven that Kaiba is alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can concentrate in the duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... it's already time for you to reveal your identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you fool me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I told you that I'm dead, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This form is more comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am "Puppeteer of the Dead", sent by Industrial Illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Yugi. Come on. Let's have some fun playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that? I knew something was happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! You don't have to hesitate anymore! Finish off this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is group A.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Blue-Eyes was destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really a mysterious thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yugi boy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Is luck part of his abilities?\N-I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:13:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me... Seto Kaiba is really alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba's terminal hacked in our Millennium server.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the moment our team invaded, he was nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. Don't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... the duel's continuity will be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's card can't be used by anyone else. Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somehow he survived the last attack, but Kaiba has one more Blue-Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... You have no monsters in play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The remaining Blue-Eyes is still in my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There won't be another miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I draw the other Blue-Eyes, my victory will be decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grappler in defense mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:14:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until the last Blue-Eyes is drawn, he will play monsters in defense mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as Seal Defense is on the field, my monsters will be in attack mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the Blue-Eyes is drawn next, it will be my loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play a face-down card on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And play Elf Swordsman in attack mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grappler is defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me in that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next I play Centaur in defense mode and set a card on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another set.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it a magic card or a trap card?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I too play a face-down card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Holy Elf in attack mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus... I do a combo with Writing of Secret Arts,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,increasing it's attack and defense by 300 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what that is but it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop these foolish things!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He has three face-down cards and three monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He increased the power of the Holy Elf to attack Centaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I draw the Blue-Eyes now....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...then his Life Points will reach zero, won't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All these face-down cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's trump will triumph?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle will be decided now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Yugi will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! My brother will surely come and do something about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that will happen {\i1}twice{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kaiba were to be doing something to this one like the previous one,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be just like the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the third Blue-Eyes didn't change at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that Kaiba isn't in any position to help you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a good feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream of Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Barrier Mirror Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:16:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trap card?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Holy Barrier will reflect the Burst Stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic card Activate! Attack Nullification!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was waiting for my trap card?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless. useless. I've seen everything beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a trump!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Resurrection of The Dead card!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be that you plan to revive my Blue-Eyes, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card that I will revive is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba's card!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have thought that got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they have the same power...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Holy Elf has been chanting a magic spell since she appeared on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That spell lets it lend it's Attack Points to another monster in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes's attack is really nearly invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that quantity of points, 3000, is not definitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all depends of the battle's situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Kaiba taught me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute... That can't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself! This is Kaiba's anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Burst Stream!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stole Kaiba's deck and soiled his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind Crush!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My voice filled with anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You used a fake to soil Seto Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will never forgive you! Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could feel an amazing Power of Darkness, Yugi-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to battle with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day that I will destroy you with these hands will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it... Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man... For a moment, I wondered what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-kun is not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning with revenge after losing to Jounouchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai Kujaku uses Dinosaur Ryuzaki in order to defeat Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Yugi's advices again, it will be easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advice is {\i1}forbidden{\i0}? That way he can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Honda go to? And even Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Friendship Power! Barbarian 1 and 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:21:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.94,0:21:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:22:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
